data.description: Stunning corner spacious 1,850 sqft Townhome located in highly sorted out Mandarin Lakes. This modern house features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, 1 half bathroom, bonus loft (which can be converted into 4th bedroom) & one car garage. Oversize lot with long driveway (long enough to park 3 cars) & with wrapped around green hedge for privacy + a Mango tree. Full accordion shutters for storm protection. Remodeled Kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Remodeled Bathrooms. Clubhouse features Large Pool, Gym, Recreational area, Child Play area & Banquet room. Association also includes Cable, Internet, 24 hour security patrol and alarm. Close to turnpike, Baptist hospital, Black Point Park & Marina, shopping centers, restaurants and much more! May the FORCE be with you!
